---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Now - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="当前在做什么" />
		<style>
			.now-shell {
				background: #fff;
				border: 1px solid rgba(176, 74, 37, 0.18);
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 1.2rem 1.3rem;
				box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
			}
			.now-list {
				padding-left: 1.1rem;
				margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
			}
			.now-list li {
				margin: 0.36rem 0;
			}
			.updated {
				font-size: 0.86rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Now</h1>
			<section class="now-shell">
				<p>这个页面用于记录我当前在推进的事情，会不定期更新。</p>
				<ul class="now-list">
					<li>优化个人写作工作流，从灵感采集到周更长文发布。</li>
					<li>持续观察 AI 对知识工作分工方式的影响。</li>
					<li>打磨“可复用思考模板”，提升表达效率与深度。</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="updated">更新时间：2026-05-09</p>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
